# Working drafts — not for repo
_temp/*
!_temp/.gitkeep

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Personal context filled during onboarding
# Uncomment these if you want to prevent personal data from being committed
# after onboarding has been run:
#
# CLAUDE.md           ← contains your name, role, company, KPIs
# GOALS.md            ← contains your personal goals
# Tasks/active.md     ← contains your real tasks
# Tasks/backlog.md
# Tasks/follow-ups.md
# Knowledge/People/   ← contains stakeholder profiles
# Projects/           ← contains real campaign briefs
#
# Keep these commented while the repo is still a template (placeholders only).
# Uncomment ONLY if you've personalised the OS and want to share a sanitised version.

# Verdict files (generated artifacts — optional to commit)
# *.brief-review-passed
# *.campaign-readiness-passed
# *.experiment-readiness-passed
